{"word":"G5202 - ὑδροποτέω - hydropotéō - hoo-drop-ot-eh'-o - Drink water","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑδροποτέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hydropotéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoo-drop-ot-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Drink water</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தண்ணீர் குடி"},{"paragraph":"to drink water"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5204 - ὕδωρ - hýdōr - hoo'-dore/5204\">G5204</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4095 - πίνω - pínō - pee'-no/4095\">G4095</a>; to <i>be</i> a <i>water drinker</i>, that is, to <i>abstain from vinous beverages:</i> - drink water.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}